OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FSome showers
OL,6,Fat first but these dying out through
OL,7,Fthe evening. Staying mostly dry
OL,8,Fovernight and largely cloudy, but a
OL,9,Ffew clear spells in places.
OL,10,
OL,11,CSunday:FCloudy in the morning with a
OL,12,Ffew showers. Again showers becoming
OL,13,Fmore frequent from late morning
OL,14,Fonwards in the southwest.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FBright
OL,17,For sunny spells and a few showers
OL,18,Fthrough the start of the week.
OL,19,FRemaining cooler.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
